      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds good in theory, but \"pseudonymization\" isn't the same as full anonymization. If someone were to cross-reference this dataset with a public registry, couldn't individual identities still be recovered? I need to know if there is any technical possibility of re-identification before I sign off on this.",
